title: Wiz Khalifa - 28 Grams [Mixtape 2014]
description: After a few delays and a quick run in with the law, Wiz Khalifa releases his new project #28Grams alongside DJ Drama & DatPiff.com. The mixtape consists of 28 records, 25 brand new and exclusive to this project. Features include Taylor Gang brethren Chevy Woods, Ty$ and Berner. Production from heavy hitters like Sonny Digital, Metro Boomin, 808 Mafia, Sledgren & more. Follow @WizKhalifa. #28Grams
